# Force LF line endings on all text source files so editors and CI on different
# platforms (Linux, macOS, Windows) can't drift the working tree into mixed
# CRLF/LF state. Without this, web-session edits to historically-CRLF files
# produced 1k-line "phantom" diffs.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.py text eol=lf
*.toml text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf

# Binary types should never be normalized.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
